{
  "lyrics": [
    {
      "start": 30,
      "end": 57.760000000000005,
      "text": "I dream in force forever, bleed through spaces, see you drifting past the fall, but no one\u0027s",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 57.76,
      "end": 69.6,
      "text": "told you where to go.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 69.6,
      "end": 89.36,
      "text": "We dive through crystal waters, perfect oceans, but no one\u0027s told me not to breathe, and all",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 89.36,
      "end": 103.52,
      "text": "the worrylessness recedes.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 103.52,
      "end": 111.6,
      "text": "Marmile those eyes like fire, I\u0027m a winged insect, you\u0027re a funeral pyre.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 111.6,
      "end": 119.75999999999999,
      "text": "Come now, bite through these wires, I\u0027m a working earth and the gods grove tired.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 119.75999999999999,
      "end": 127.84,
      "text": "Reset my passion, violets along both lines of a pathway higher.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 127.84,
      "end": 135.51999999999998,
      "text": "Grow back your sharpest teeth, you know my desire.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 135.52,
      "end": 143.68,
      "text": "All will travel far beyond the path of reason.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 143.68,
      "end": 162.8,
      "text": "Take me back to Eden, take me back to Eden.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 162.8,
      "end": 172.96,
      "text": "Take me back to Eden.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 192.8,
      "end": 205.52,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, I spit blood when I wake up, sink porcelain, stain, choke, cannot bring matter",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 205.52,
      "end": 206.52,
      "text": "and make up.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 206.52,
      "end": 210.8,
      "text": "Just two days since the mainframe went down and I\u0027m still messed up.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 210.8,
      "end": 215.92000000000002,
      "text": "Room feels like a knee-freezer, I dangling like po\u0027 cuts, missed calls.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 215.92000000000002,
      "end": 218.96,
      "text": "Answer phones from people I just don\u0027t trust.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 218.96,
      "end": 223.92000000000002,
      "text": "Nerd talk, train club, but I\u0027ll take a pond of your flesh before you take a piece of my",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 223.92000000000002,
      "end": 224.92000000000002,
      "text": "paste up.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 224.92000000000002,
      "end": 233.68,
      "text": "White roses, black doves, godmother, rise up, I need you to see me for what I have become.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 233.68,
      "end": 241.84,
      "text": "Marmile those eyes like fire, I\u0027m a winged insect, you\u0027re a funeral pyre.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
