      "text": "No amount of love will keep it around if we don\u0027t choose it.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 329.28,
      "end": 345.59999999999997,
      "text": "And I don\u0027t know what it\u0027s got its teeth in me, but I\u0027m about to bite by an anger.",
      "IsActive": false
    },
    {
      "start": 345.6,
